name: Simone
description: This is a policeman Simone, he has been with the police for 6 years. Once he covered a large gang, for which he was given an honorary award, but in this gang was his brother Gustavo, who also had to be imprisoned. After that, he started having problems with his families, his mother considers him a traitor, and his brother does not want to talk to him, which is why he began to drink a lot, and now he hates his reward.
